PrecisAmendments to the FEDERAL ELECTIONS FEES TARIFF that will modify the Tariff with respect to the remuneration of Returning Officers who perform tasks related to the establishment of polling divisions, make wording changes recommended by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations and will provide for rate changes to various positions.

precis:
Amendments to the FEDERAL ELECTIONS FEES TARIFF that will modify the Tariff
with respect to the remuneration of Returning Officers who perform tasks
related to the establishment of polling divisions, make wording changes
recommended by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations
and will provide for rate changes to various positions.
